Title: SDS 209: Full-Time Data Scientist after just 1 year in the field
Description: In this episode of the SuperDataScience Podcast, I chat with the aspiring Data Scientist, Rio Branham, who now has a full-time job as a data scientist after just 1 year in the field. You will learn about the difference between data science and econometrics, what kind of tools and techniques Rio uses and what his aspirations are. You will also hear about Rio’s approach to learning which together with Rio's mindset, make this a very inspirational podcast episode. Rio makes a reckless commitment for 2019 right on this podcast.If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at www.superdatascience.com/209
